@trhoden

to make this more general, perhaps two computed props representing the "start" and "end" of a line?

E.g.

```javascript
{
  alignStart() {
    return Vue.bidi === 'rtl' ? 'right' : 'left';
  },
  alignEnd() {
    return Vue.bidi === 'ltr' ? 'right' : 'left';
  },
}
```
